🎃👻 Join us this Thursday for a spooktacular night for Nappy Halloween x OUT THE BOX! Get ready for some frightful fun and a chance to win a $150 cash prize for the best costume! 

🕗 When: This Thursday 
📍 Where: Atlantucky 
🎟️ Cost: Free w/t RSVP!

Don’t miss out on a night filled with great vibes, awesome people, and amazing music brought to you by @gallery85atl and @nappyroots . We can’t wait to see your creative costumes! If you haven’t, go listen to @nappyroots new single “Howlin’ At The Moon” on all streaming platforms. 🧙‍♀️✨ 

RSVP now and let’s make this Halloween unforgettable! 🎉
